### Low Pressure Laminates and Particle Boards
**Notice Reference Number:** WS3823344777-Doc3824838068
**Solicitation Number:** WS3823344777
**Tender Closing Date:** February 6, 2023 at 14:00 EST

### Notice Information
**Notice Type:** Request for Standing Offer (RFSO)
**Procurement Method:** Competitive - Open Bidding
**Duration Contract:** March 1, 2023 to March 31, 2024, with an additional four one-year option periods

### Definitions and Description
Low Pressure Laminates (plastic laminate) and particle board are required by Correctional Services of Canada's (CSC) CORCAN program. The goods will be supplied and delivered to various locations across Canada on an as-and-when requested basis.

### Detailed Specifications
A detailed solicitation document is available that includes specifications, mandatory requirements, and delivery logistics. Official solicitation documents may be submitted in either official language of Canada.

### Evaluation Criteria
The following criteria will be evaluated for compliance. The bidder's ability to meet mandatory requirements and to fulfill the terms and conditions will be evaluated.

### Notice Documents
Documents may be downloaded from the Government of Canada Federal Institution's etendering website: [http://discovery.ariba.com/rfx/15116705?extsite=MTUxMTY3MDVfQU4wMTQ4NDA1MDk5Mg==](http://discovery.ariba.com/rfx/15116705?extsite=MTUxMTY3MDVfQU4wMTQ4NDA1MDk5Mg==)

### Contact Information

Arboleda, Ian (PSPC)
Email: [ian.arboleda@tpsgc-pwgsc.gc.ca](mailto:ian.arboleda@tpsgc-pwgsc.gc.ca)
Phone: Not stated
Fax: Not stated
Address: 11 Laurier street, Gatineau, Quebec, K1A 0S5 Canada.
Please contact with specific information requirements regarding this procurement.
